711115f-a.title: Manhattan: 11th Street (West) - Hudson Street
711115f-a.text:
West 11th (formerly Hammond) Street, east from Hudson Street, the
view cut off by St. Vincent's Hospital at the N.W. corner of Seventh
Avenue and the true 11th Street. 295 West 11th Street, the new
6-story Abingdon Arms apartment house shown here on the N.E.
corner, has quite recently replaced old 299-97-95-93 West 11th
Street.
May 20, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO RRPnODDUCTIONS.
